attributes.title: Covered in hot Cheeto dust😾
attributes.review: It was nice outside 🌍so I went to ride my dog 🐶and walk my bike🚲 when I got a text📱 from my friend 🧑🏻about this app. He was 𝗘𝗫𝗧𝗥𝗘𝗠𝗘𝗟𝗬 upset😤 and said 🗣as soon as he downloaded this app he saw a big fat NAKED Cheeto outside his window racing 🏃🏾💨 his pet turtle🐢! he then went on to tell me all the h͟o͟r͟r͟i͟b͟l͟e͟ things this app did. I looked at my calendar📆 and it said July 8th so I thought my friend was pulling an April fools prank on me so I went to see how bad👎🏾 this app was for my self. As soon as the app finished downloading my bike started growling and barking and seemed very upset😾. So I looked around to see what it was so worried about, and saw a naked Cheeto on a tricycle coming right for us so I put my helmet on and road my dog home as fast 🏃🏾‍♀️as I could. I was very 🆂🆆🅴🅰︎🆃🆈from the ride so I took a shower 💦and turned the water on hot🔥 Then all of a sudden hot Cheeto dust started pouring out all over me 👿I knew there was only one 1️⃣thing causing all this commotion so I grabbed my phone ☎️and deleted the app but as soon as I pressed delete it multiplied¡!✖️ so I kept pressing delete over and over again and now I have 50 MILLION folders of this horrible app ᔕTᑌᑕK on my phone😡. I knew there was only one thing that could be done so I threw my phone in my fridge and baked it until it was nice and crispy. I was so angry  😤 that my phone was ruined and that this app destroyed my whole day so I grabbed my toaster and typed up this review as fast as I could.⚠️ !DO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS APP!⚠️
